changelog: multimail 2.2.0 (2009-11-22)
  * module editor.py improved (but we've lost some features)

changelog: multimail 2.2.1 (2011-06-14)
  * rewrite of module editor.py
  * general refactoring
  * added some option and deleted others
  * enable use of config file
  * some tweak on temporary archive creation for attachments
  * tests improved
  * other stuffs

changelog: multimail 2.2.2 (2011-07-09)
  * needs at least python2.6 (won't work with python2.5 anymore)
  * try to be compatible from python2.6 to python3.x
    (actually the *editor* module won't work on python3, need fix)
  * test improved
  * other stuff
